# Component Patterns

Reference: `.mba-template/design-systems/*/components.md` for detailed patterns

## Button

### Variants (choose 3-4)
- **Primary/Filled**: Solid background, high emphasis
- **Secondary/Outlined**: Border, medium emphasis
- **Tertiary/Ghost**: No border, low emphasis
- **Danger/Destructive**: Red, for delete/remove actions

### Sizes
- **Small**: 28-32px height
- **Medium**: 36-40px height (default)
- **Large**: 44-48px height

### Structure
```html
<button class="btn btn-primary btn-medium">
  <!-- Use icon library (Font Awesome, Heroicons, etc.) - NEVER generate SVG -->
  <i class="fa-solid fa-save" aria-hidden="true"></i>
  <span>Button Text</span>
</button>
```

**IMPORTANT**: See `.cursor/rules/15-icons-assets.mdc` - Always use icon libraries, never generate SVG code.

### States
- Default, Hover, Active, Focus, Disabled, Loading

### Focus State
- 2px outline, primary color
- 2px offset from button
- Visible on keyboard navigation

## Input Fields

### Types
- Text, Email, Password, Number, Tel, URL, Search, Textarea

### Structure
```html
<div class="form-field">
  <label for="input-id">Label</label>
  <input type="text" id="input-id" placeholder="Placeholder">
  <span class="help-text">Help text</span>
  <span class="error-text">Error message</span>
</div>
```

### Sizes
- **Small**: 32px height
- **Medium**: 40px height (default)
- **Large**: 48px height

### States
- Default, Hover, Focus, Error, Disabled, Read-only

### Validation
- Inline validation on blur
- Error message below field
- Error icon in field (optional)
- Red border on error

## Card

### Structure
```html
<div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h3>Title</h3>
    <button>Action</button>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    Content
  </div>
  <div class="card-footer">
    <button>Cancel</button>
    <button>Save</button>
  </div>
</div>
```

### Variants
- **Flat**: Border only, no shadow
- **Elevated**: Subtle shadow
- **Interactive**: Hover state, clickable

### Spacing
- Padding: 16-24px
- Header to body: 12-16px
- Body to footer: 16px

## Table

### Structure
```html
<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Column 1</th>
      <th>Column 2</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>Data 1</td>
      <td>Data 2</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
```

### Features
- Sortable columns (with icon)
- Row hover state
- Selected row state
- Pagination
- Empty state

### Spacing
- Cell padding: 8-12px horizontal, 8-12px vertical
- Row height: 40-48px
- Header background: Subtle gray

## Modal/Dialog

### Structure
```html
<div class="modal-overlay">
  <div class="modal">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <h2>Title</h2>
      <button aria-label="Close">×</button>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      Content
    </div>
    <div class="modal-footer">
      <button>Cancel</button>
      <button>Confirm</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```

### Sizes
- Small: 400-480px
- Medium: 600px (default)
- Large: 800-960px
- Full: 90% viewport

### Behavior
- Overlay dims background (rgba(0,0,0,0.5))
- Center on screen
- Trap focus inside modal
- Escape to close (if safe)
- Return focus on close

## Navigation

### Top Navigation
```html
<nav class="top-nav">
  <div class="nav-brand">Logo</div>
  <ul class="nav-menu">
    <li><a href="#">Link 1</a></li>
    <li><a href="#">Link 2</a></li>
  </ul>
  <div class="nav-actions">
    <button>Sign In</button>
  </div>
</nav>
```

### Side Navigation
```html
<aside class="side-nav">
  <nav>
    <ul>
      <li class="active">
        <icon />
        <span>Dashboard</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <icon />
        <span>Settings</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </nav>
</aside>
```

### Mobile Navigation
- Hamburger menu (top-left or top-right)
- Full-screen overlay or slide-in drawer
- Bottom tab bar (3-5 items)

## Form Layout

### Vertical (Default)
```html
<form>
  <div class="form-field">
    <label>First Name</label>
    <input type="text">
  </div>
  <div class="form-field">
    <label>Last Name</label>
    <input type="text">
  </div>
  <div class="form-actions">
    <button type="button">Cancel</button>
    <button type="submit">Submit</button>
  </div>
</form>
```

### Horizontal (Compact)
```html
<div class="form-field-horizontal">
  <label>Label</label>
  <input type="text">
</div>
```

### Multi-Column (Desktop)
```html
<div class="form-grid">
  <div class="form-field">...</div>
  <div class="form-field">...</div>
</div>
```

## Dropdown/Select

### Structure
```html
<div class="dropdown">
  <button class="dropdown-trigger">
    Select Option
    <icon name="chevron-down" />
  </button>
  <div class="dropdown-menu">
    <button class="dropdown-item">Option 1</button>
    <button class="dropdown-item">Option 2</button>
  </div>
</div>
```

### Behavior
- Click to open
- Click outside to close
- Arrow keys to navigate
- Enter to select
- Escape to close

## Toast/Notification

### Structure
```html
<div class="toast toast-success">
  <icon name="check" />
  <div class="toast-content">
    <strong>Success</strong>
    <p>Action completed successfully</p>
  </div>
  <button aria-label="Close">×</button>
</div>
```

### Types
- Success (green)
- Error (red)
- Warning (orange)
- Info (blue)

### Position
- Top-right (common)
- Top-center
- Bottom-right
- Bottom-center

### Duration
- 3-5 seconds (auto-dismiss)
- Persistent (manual dismiss)

## Badge

### Sizes
- Small: 16px height
- Medium: 20px height
- Large: 24px height

### Variants
- Filled (solid background)
- Outlined (border only)
- Dot (small indicator)

### Usage
- Status indicators
- Notification counts
- Category labels

## Tabs

### Structure
```html
<div class="tabs">
  <div class="tab-list" role="tablist">
    <button role="tab" aria-selected="true">Tab 1</button>
    <button role="tab">Tab 2</button>
  </div>
  <div class="tab-panel" role="tabpanel">
    Content 1
  </div>
</div>
```

### Styles
- Underline (active indicator below)
- Filled (active has background)
- Boxed (tabs look like tabs)

## Accordion

### Structure
```html
<div class="accordion">
  <div class="accordion-item">
    <button class="accordion-header">
      <span>Section 1</span>
      <icon name="chevron-down" />
    </button>
    <div class="accordion-content">
      Content 1
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```

### Behavior
- Click to expand/collapse
- Chevron rotates
- Smooth animation
- Single or multiple open

## Best Practices

### Do
- Use semantic HTML
- Include all interactive states
- Provide keyboard navigation
- Add ARIA labels
- Show loading states
- Handle empty states
- Display error states
- Use consistent sizing
- Follow platform patterns

### Don't
- Use divs for buttons
- Forget focus states
- Ignore keyboard users
- Skip loading indicators
- Use color alone for status
- Make components too complex
- Ignore accessibility
- Reinvent standard patterns
